            "id": 6142201,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉台積電帶隊拉尾盤大漲314點衝向歷史高點 周線連2紅",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (5) 日開高走高，由台積電領軍電子權值股衝鋒，推升指數終場收在最高點 24494.58 點，漲幅達 314.73 點，距離歷史高點 24570.58 僅差 76 點，成交量則較昨日下降，約 4163 億元，本周一共上漲 261.48 點，周線連 2 紅。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6142201/l/0c7da0c872019a87ea51b647628378a3.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉電子權值帶頭衝 大漲314點收最高 周線連2紅。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>權值股普遍走強，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 最後一盤買盤湧現，帶動股價收在最高點 1180 元，上漲近 2%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 小漲 1% 表態，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 獲資金青睞，一路走高至 1435 元，大漲近 4%，創一個多月來新高。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其他權值股表現也亮眼，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 收在 726 元，飆漲半根漲停板，企圖挑戰前高 730 元，市值達 1.88 兆元，日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASX-US</a>) 漲幅超過 1%，智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>)、緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>) 也都有 3-4% 的漲幅，漲勢相當凌厲。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體族群今日強勢出頭，包括華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、晶豪科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3006:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3006\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3006-TW</a>) 與群聯 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8299-TW</a>) 全面亮燈漲停，鈺創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5351:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5351\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5351-TW</a>)、宇瞻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)、威剛 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>) 也都有 5% 左右的漲幅。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
